data.title: Children's Healthcare Pen Paws program connects patients to service dogs
data.meta_description: For the past 13 years, Reggie and his fellow pups have made fast friends and provided comfort to hundreds of little patients at Children's Healthcare of Atlanta. Now patients can stay connected to their favorite service dog even when they're not around through a Pen Paws program.
